1. Create an abstract class Calculator having add, and substract methods. 
Also create a functional interface having sum method. 
The Calculator class is meant to for calculating two numbers. 
Create a class Basic_calculator that adds, subtracts, multiplies and divides two numbers.
Create a class Advanced_calculator that finds that performs the any two bitwise operations on those two numbers.
Create objects of those classes. Use the concept of dynamic method dispatch. 
In the main method, make the use of lambda function to find the sum of three numbers.


